OL,3,CInquest told of 'heroic efforts' to
OL,4,Csave people trapped in burning
OL,5,Chelicopter
OL,7,FPolice officers made "heroic efforts"
OL,8,Fto reach five people trapped in a
OL,9,Fhelicopter which was engulfed in a
OL,10,F"wall of flames" after crashing
OL,11,Foutside the King Power Stadium in
OL,12,FLeicester, an inquest has heard.
OL,14,FFive people, including Leicester City
OL,15,FFC owner Vichai Srivaddhanaprabha,
OL,16,Freferred to as Khun Vichai in court,
OL,17,Fwere killed when the Leonardo AW169
OL,18,Fhelicopter spun out of control as it
OL,19,Fwas leaving the pitch after a match on
OL,20,F27 October 2018.
