OL,3,CInquest told of 'heroic efforts' to
OL,4,Csave people trapped in burning
OL,5,Chelicopter
OL,7,F"It was a flash that caught my
OL,8,Fattention. I could see the helicopter
OL,9,Fwas rotating and it was horizontal and
OL,10,Fmoving around, and that movement drew
OL,11,Fmy attention to it", Sgt Hooper told
OL,12,Fthe hearing. "We heard a loud crunch,
OL,13,Fa metallic sound, which indicated to
OL,14,Fme it had crashed."
OL,16,FThe sergeant described a "wall of
OL,17,Fflames" at the centre of the
OL,18,Fhelicopter when he reached it, and he
OL,19,Fused a baton to hit the windscreen.
