OL,3,CInquest told of 'heroic efforts' to
OL,4,Csave people trapped in burning
OL,5,Chelicopter
OL,7,F"Every time I hit it it bounced off
OL,8,Fand was repelling my baton every time.
OL,9,FThere was some slow movement from the
OL,10,Fpilot, possibly because he was dazed",
OL,11,Fhe said.
OL,13,F"It was incredibly hot at that point,
OL,14,Fthe heat was pretty much unbearable.
OL,15,FThe aircraft was popping and banging `
OL,16,FI did not know how long it was going
OL,17,Fto be before it went up."
