OL,3,CInquest told of 'heroic efforts' to
OL,4,Csave people trapped in burning
OL,5,Chelicopter
OL,7,FLeicestershire Fire and Rescue station
OL,8,Fmanager Chris Parsons told the inquest
OL,9,Fit would have been a "significant
OL,10,Fchallenge" and "potentially not
OL,11,Fpossible" without time to extinguish
OL,12,Fthe fire.
OL,14,FPhilip Shepherd KC, representing the
OL,15,Frelatives of Khun Vichai, told the
OL,16,Fofficers: "On behalf of the family of
OL,17,FKhun Vichai can I congratulate you on
OL,18,Fthe heroic efforts you made that night
OL,19,Fto try to save the lives of the people
OL,20,Fwho tragically died."
