OL,3,CInquest told of 'heroic efforts' to
OL,4,Csave people trapped in burning
OL,5,Chelicopter
OL,7,FJohn Ledwidge, former grounds manager
OL,8,Fat Leicester City, told the inquest he
OL,9,Fsaw the moment the aircraft caught
OL,10,Ffire after it "aggressively" spun to
OL,11,Fthe ground.
OL,13,FHe added that club owner Khun Vichai
OL,14,Fwas an "investor in people's dreams",
OL,15,Fadding, "he touched a lot of people
OL,16,Fwith his generosity, his warmth and
OL,17,Fhumour. I felt like I was part of the
OL,18,Ffamily."
